# Notion integration token (from https://www.notion.so/my-integrations)
# One shared token across every connector — see connectors.json for
# per-page Notion page IDs and Apps Script URLs, which are NOT env vars.
NOTION_TOKEN=

# Vercel Blob: no manual env var needed here for production. Vercel auto-injects
# BLOB_STORE_ID and a short-lived VERCEL_OIDC_TOKEN at runtime once a Blob store
# is connected to this project (Storage tab > Connect Blob store). The
# @vercel/blob SDK picks these up automatically — do not hardcode a token.
# For LOCAL dev only, run `vercel env pull` to fetch working values, or set a
# static BLOB_READ_WRITE_TOKEN from the store's dashboard if your store still
# uses the legacy static-token mode.
# BLOB_READ_WRITE_TOKEN=


